Dear Mr. Fauze Polpeta:

Congratulations - your paper 'Portabilidade em Sistemas Operacionais
Baseados em Componentes de Software' for SBC 2004 WSO has been accepted.

The reviews are below or can be found at
http://soyuz.metropoa.tche.br/PaperShow.cgi?m=3037.

The deadline for the camera ready version of your paper is 28/May/2004.
Specific instructions will be available starting on May 18th at
http://www.lasid.ufba.br/wso2004/. Please address the concerns of the
reviewers when preparing the camera ready paper.

We are looking forward to your presentation in the Workshop de Sistemas
Operacionais. We would appreciate to know as soon as possible who among
the authors is planning on doing the presentation. Please let us know by
