Dear Mr. Thiago Santos:

The "Workshop em Sistemas Operacionais" received 36 submissions, and
were able to accept only 12 papers.

Unfortunately, your paper #3407 (An application-oriented
parallel-programming system for dedicated cluster computing) could not
